## Notes

- Estimates in this packet are **not** a CMAQ application. They are a
  cycle-readiness diagnostic the lead agency uses to focus effort on
  candidates whose emissions-reduction estimates and cost-effectiveness
  values can survive FHWA / state DOT review before the full
  application package is assembled.
- Every estimate in this packet is mirrored as a
  `cmaq_emissions_estimate` fact_block (plus one `cmaq_portfolio_summary`)
  appended to this run's `fact_blocks.jsonl`, so subsequent narrative
  and chat turns remain subject to the ClawModeler citation contract.

